ZH: 我会用真诚的友谊来回报你的帮助。
EN: I will repay your help with genuine friendship.

ZH: 你的慷慨之举我一定会回报的。
EN: I will definitely repay your generosity.

ZH: 父母的养育之恩，孩子应该用孝顺来回报。
EN: Children should repay their parents' upbringing with filial piety.

ZH: 他发誓会用成绩来回报老师对他的信任。
EN: He vowed to repay the teacher's trust with his achievements.

ZH: 她利用自己的才华来回报社会。
EN: She uses her talent to repay society.

ZH: 感恩节是一个回报他人善意的节日。
EN: Thanksgiving is a holiday to repay others' kindness.

ZH: 谢谢你的爱和支持，我一定会努力回报。
EN: Thank you for your love and support, I will work hard to repay.

ZH: 我要靠努力工作来回报父母的养育之恩。
EN: I will repay my parents' upbringing by working hard.

ZH: 对不起，我无法用金钱回报你所做的一切。
EN: I'm sorry, I can't repay everything you've done with money.

ZH: 因为得到过别人的帮助，我决心要回报社会。
EN: Because I have received help from others, I am determined to repay society.

ZH: 用爱心和关怀回报弱者是我们的责任。
EN: It is our responsibility to repay the weak with love and care.

ZH: 请接受我最诚挚的感谢，我无法用言语回报你。
EN: Please accept my most sincere thanks, I cannot repay you with words.

ZH: 我会尽我最大的努力来回报你对我的支持。
EN: I will do my best to repay your support.

ZH: 他用努力工作来回报自己的父母。
EN: He repays his parents with hard work.

ZH: 报答他人的恩情是我们应尽的责任。
EN: Repaying others' kindness is our duty.

ZH: 这个孩子用学业和事业回报了他的父母。
EN: This child repaid his parents with academic and career success.

ZH: 无论发生什么事情，我一定要回报你对我的一切。
EN: No matter what happens, I will repay you for everything you have done for me.

ZH: 他用行动来回报对方的善意。
EN: He repays the other party's kindness with actions.

ZH: 在这个世界上，我们要努力回报社会的恩情。
EN: In this world, we should strive to repay society's kindness.

ZH: 做一个善良的人，用爱心回报这个世界。
EN: Be a kind person and repay this world with love.
